prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, flat 2D vector illustration of the couple from the reference photo, ID 9d620ae8-71b8-41b9-bb6e-fdfd0cb3cc35, transformed into simple cartoon characters. The scene is a funny and surreal combination of their interests. Jordan, wearing his gray jacket over a plain burgundy shirt, is dynamically posed mid-air on a snowboard. Instead of a snowy mountain, he is snowboarding down a giant California roll. Lao Lao, wearing her light-colored jacket and glasses, stands at the bottom of the "sushi slope," laughing with a joyful expression and holding a pair of giant chopsticks as if she's about to catch him. The California roll is simplified, with clean lines showing the rice, avocado, and crab stick layers. A few minimalist salmon roe and wasabi details are scattered around the base of the slope. The background is a solid, clean, light pastel blue. In the center, below the action, is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script. The entire composition is clean, playful, and focused on the characters' humorous interaction.
